    "During his tenure at the Modern, Rubin acquired Picasso's ''Charnel House'' (1944-45), Miro's ''Birth of the World'' (1925) and two 1950's cutouts by Matisse, ''Memory of Oceania'' and ''The Swimming Pool.''": [
